title: Changes to Question Time to focus on local issues (Prime Minister of Australia)
text: ( Source : Prime Minister of Australia ) The Australian House of Representatives will trial a new Constituency Question Time that will give Members an opportunity to ask specific questions relating to their electorates and the matters raised
